commit.message:
Changed Dockerfile to resolve deps using pipenv/Pipefile(.lock) before pip3->setup.py for httpbin.

Also added Pipfile(.lock) prior to the remaining source, improving Docker image cacheability.

Git is also required to fetch pyyaml.

This results in more deterministic and reproducible image builds, since httpbin dependencies
are installed using locked versions from Pipfile.lock before httpbin is itself installed.

Fixed #493.

commit.message:
Revert "Support `show_env` param in `/headers`", reverting #457. Fixed #487.

The docstring typo fixes are retained, along with the additional tests,
modified to revert to the original "headers": { dict format.

The reverted change get_dict('headers') -> get_headers() was not required. The
query-string ?show_env=1 was already effective in allowing env headers to be
returned.

This partially reverts commit 31ffe79981a079d6605352d2d84de2f2d27ab6db.
